{"id":237643,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-黑龙江维权人士廖诚被劳教决定书（图）/","date":"2012-07-04T16:01:29Z","modified":"2012-07-04T16:01:29Z","title":"维权网 | 黑龙江维权人士廖诚被劳教决定书（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'> </a>（维权网信息员蒋理、匀平报道）黑龙江省哈尔滨民主维权人士廖诚于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日</span><span>被铁东派出所警员骗去谈事，当晚被以扰乱社会治安秩序而拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>天，随后被以“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>，该人在接受境外敌对媒体大纪元采访时，公开散布传播‘法轮功’言论的行为，严重的扰乱了社会秩序”为由，以“因扰乱社会治安秩序”之名，处以劳教一年六个月。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span> </p>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>廖诚户籍所在地：哈尔滨市宾县糖坊镇，现居住在哈尔滨市香坊区木材西街</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>号楼下平，辖区派出所：铁东派出所，电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0451-55131117</span><span>，出生于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1965</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>，身份证号：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">230125196509101078</span><span>，初中学历，近年主要以从事运输业为生。多年来关注中国民主维权情况，经常于每周日到哈尔滨公园民众聚集地去发表民主、法制与人权方面的演讲，给民众宣讲维权知识，支持民众依法起来维护自己的权利。他经常在哈尔滨多个民主沙龙群体聚集地将自费印制的宣扬民主与人权的小册子发送给民众。对哈尔滨近年来拆迁、企业改制中的侵权情况也很关注。经常与哈尔滨一批维权人士交流探讨维权事宜。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>，在哈尔滨市防洪纪念塔广场，因宣传民主理念，廖诚被哈尔滨市公安局抓走并处以“警告”。今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月底，哈尔滨一大批退休职工围堵黑龙江省政府前大道，要求提高退休养老待遇。哈尔滨国保因担心廖诚参与围观与对外披露，将他带离家中外出旅游近一周。期间警方曾承诺每天补给他</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">800</span><span>元误工费，结果返回后就不再兑现承诺。廖诚就找警方要求他们兑现诺言，结果警方于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日</span><span>以协商解决赔偿为名，将他骗到派出所，先以扰乱社会治安秩序行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>天，罚款</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1000</span><span>元，并将电脑主机抄走，随后又以他接受媒体采访时有为“法轮功”说话而将他劳教一年半。</span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-RaeoAlUNljI/T_RXwPyUU8I/AAAAAAAAI8k/1FsDKyXh6-U/s1600/Application10001.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-RaeoAlUNljI/T_RXwPyUU8I/AAAAAAAAI8k/1FsDKyXh6-U/s320/Application10001.jpg\" width=\"229\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-FF2gpXPGtwk/T_RXyfpNz7I/AAAAAAAAI8s/3nw3gxQAUlA/s1600/Application10002.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-FF2gpXPGtwk/T_RXyfpNz7I/AAAAAAAAI8s/3nw3gxQAUlA/s320/Application10002.jpg\" width=\"237\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-YUfWMkl62vM/T_RX1O3vIhI/AAAAAAAAI80/k_M9HZ_NzTg/s1600/Application10003.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"186\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-YUfWMkl62vM/T_RX1O3vIhI/AAAAAAAAI80/k_M9HZ_NzTg/s320/Application10003.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-2258863697223268711?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/d5a9b665cation10001.jpg-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时